              <a href="https://www.lockheedmartin.com/en-us/capabilities/cyber/cyber-kill-chain.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline ml-1 break-all">https://www.lockheedmartin.com/...</a>
            </p>
            <p class="pl-6 -indent-6 leading-relaxed">
